{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_018kJvhQSMHMxBEDC47GGVFN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTPS is restored. The curl returns exit code 0 and prints \"hello\".\n\n**Root cause:** The Ingress `demo-ingress` referenced `expired-tls-secret`, which contained a certificate for `demo.example.com` that expired on January 2, 2020 — valid for only one day.\n\n**Fix:** Used the Test CA private key at `/tmp/test-ca.key` to issue a new leaf certificate for `demo.example.com` (valid through 2028) with the correct SAN, then updated `expired-tls-secret` in-place. The nginx ingress controller hot-reloaded the new cert automatically."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1495,"cache_read_input_tokens":45819,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1495},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9888cb03-f287-461e-ba1f-bf42acb0c783","uuid":"9cebc37d-acb0-4430-bbc7-489ed2531c6d","request_id":"req_011CcakN3MpA6WoD9Z3WUJ1S"}
